Package com.ee364project.exceptions

package com.ee364project.exceptions
Package for custom exceptions used throughout the EE364 project. This package contains custom exceptions that are used throughout the EE364 project. These exceptions are designed to provide a consistent and standardized way of handling errors and exceptions that may occur during the execution of the project. Overall, this package provides a standardized way of handling exceptions throughout the EE364 project, ensuring that errors are handled in a consistent and reliable manner.
